      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk. every time i think things might get better i just realize its just physics and biology and nothing else. there’s no grand plan or purpose. just a long stretch of darkness before being born and a long stretch of darkness after we die. sometimes it feels like we’re just fighting to stay alive for no reason at all.",
